Has the same appearance as Sharkjaw Cutlass.<br>
Effect: Spirit Tap<br>
STR+10 WIS+8<br>
Update: Found in Veeshan's Peak off of Silverwing!</font>
    </td>
  </tr>
  
</table><br>
